  "title": "Museum Experience Associate",
  "description": "<p>This role is perfect if you enjoy being on your feet, engaging young minds, and bringing learning to life outside the classroom.</p><p><strong>Tasks:</strong></p><ul><li>Guide and engage students during museum tours</li><li>Support museum educators during activities</li><li>Handle simple onsite enquiries and feedback</li><li>Observe and conduct evaluations of educators during tours</li></ul><p><strong>Role Details:</strong></p><ul><li>Days: Tuesday - Thursday (school term only)</li><li>Hours: 8.30am - 4.30pm (up to 3 tours/day)</li><li>Location: Central Singapore</li><li>Commitment: Minimum 6 months</li><li>Pay: $15/hour</li></ul><p><strong>We’re Looking For:</strong></p><ul><li>Friendly, confident, and approachable</li><li>Comfortable working with children</li><li>Responsible, independent, and presentable</li><li>Completed GCE A-Level / Diploma (any field)</li></ul>",
